{"data":[{"id":561222129,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"b450e65e2ca7fd5996be6db49ad013a4","url_token":"qing-zheng-30-4","name":"青争","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/b450e65e2ca7fd5996be6db49ad013a4","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561222129","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-a2a1e58383020ca02430ea11700c376c_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545928207,"updated_time":1545928930,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":16,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e1月1号见证哥德巴赫猜想猜想哈哈，虽然看了n多评论知道了成功几率差多为2的头发数次方分之一，但作为反向机会主义者（瞎编的）我觉得支持一个大家都觉得对的比较没意思。（哈哈哈假如我押对了相当于中了一个不可能得到超级彩票，不是说概率为0不等于不可能发生吗，手动狗头）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e知乎上吵翻天该鼓励或者打击这位同学，嘲讽他和嘲讽鼓励他的和嘲讽盲目嘲讽鼓励他的，再次笑话民科的，各位数学大牛发的也看不懂，假装收藏\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不过我觉得真的证明出他的错了（万一对了）给个教训就好了，真的沸如江海的评论对于一个未成年来说，还能比较镇定，我叹服他的心理素质，起码这就是很多人做不到的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e下图我起码觉得他情商不错，正常高中生应该反驳或者暴跳如雷\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-39df2fc860977a8916335b16cc64b560_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-822e2e652b064d98f952e8970f75756a_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-39df2fc860977a8916335b16cc64b560_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1080'%20height='1920'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-822e2e652b064d98f952e8970f75756a_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-39df2fc860977a8916335b16cc64b560_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-39df2fc860977a8916335b16cc64b560_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5cc12a52148676a1dce0f5c38e5763a8_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-b94a9150457450f7129d66374b6f305a_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5cc12a52148676a1dce0f5c38e5763a8_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1080'%20height='1920'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-b94a9150457450f7129d66374b6f305a_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5cc12a52148676a1dce0f5c38e5763a8_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5cc12a52148676a1dce0f5c38e5763a8_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e很多人嘲讽有智商就不应该偏科，我对大脑没研究，但也知道历史上很多偏科成才的故事。为什么以前可以，现在不行？你可以嘲讽，但是觉得别人鼓励他就是在捧杀他，未免也太对青年人苛求了吧，键盘打字容易，别人有能力让这个话题火也是你们一做出来的，说到底，说他炒作，火还不得感谢你们？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我个人觉得某些回答大牛所用讽刺手法很有情商，人活久懂得“教训”晚辈还是挺不错的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"